{"tid":1421832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［忍左好耐］中環蘭桂坊五毛餐廳 大家一定要抵制","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:03:05.000Z","uid":124810,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce480d1050ea709e55d18c2102739e98936458a","tid":1421832,"uid":124810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"巴絲們好<br />\n<br />\n最近社會氣氛太差 藍絲港豬又好多<br />\n為左大家唔好再去錯五毛餐廳 （特別係蘭桂坊/ 中環附近做野既巴絲） 所以出黎開post<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，想比大家知多一間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係位於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蘭桂坊加州大廈地下 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> &ldquo;VIVA&rdquo;</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食西班牙菜 新餐廳黎咖！！ 一入夜仲有DJ打碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以話係多元化餐廳<br />\n<br />\n可惜，背後餐廳大股東係一名大陸女士 仲要係亞視前藝人： <span style=\"font-size: large;\">李婉僮</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1jkPT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1jkPT2.png&h=5627934e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wifoNH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwifoNH2.png&h=08751cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Aa8en3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Aa8en3.png&h=8bf33f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAb3NNb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAb3NNb.png&h=28e60d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到佢係we7度鬧我地手足， 同一般藍絲廢老、大部分中國同胞思想一樣： 咩都係外國勢力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話示威者好可怕 擾亂秩序 是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一群該死的東西</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Uv0PZ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Uv0PZ5.png&h=63ab6dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYXZk6M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYXZk6M.png&h=1f2739c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkLoNMN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkLoNMN.png&h=7dd3ef5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huOBoj8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuOBoj8.png&h=432676ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地每人每日行一小步 罷食呢間五毛餐廳 <br />\n<br />\n希望呢間野早日執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果中意食野既巴絲記得記得唔好幫襯佢，唔好比佢賺我哋嘅血汗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}